                                        <h1 class="a-header__title">Self-isolation is triggering my eating disorder and this is how I&#x27;m coping</h1>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        <div class="a-header__wrapper">
                            <div class="a-header__content">

                                    <div class="a-header__teaser"><p class="bb-p">How one woman's recovery is being affected by the pandemic.</p></div>

