                                                        <h3 class="c-card__title">
                                                            <span>This is why you&#x27;re feeling so groggy and struggling to sleep during self-isolation</span>
                                                        </h3>

                                                        <p class="c-card__teaser">
                                                            Here are expert-backed hacks to up your energy.
                                                        </p>

                                                    <hr class="c-card__separator" />
