                                    <article class="c-card c-card--switcher">
                                            <a href="/article/samantha-cristoforetti-astronaut-isolation-tips" class="c-card__link c-card__link--article ">I&#x27;m a female astronaut who spent 199 days in space and here are my most empowering self-isolation tips</a>

                                        <div class="c-card__obj">
                                            <div class="c-card__obj__header">
